َةٍ","english":"The orphaned relative,","roots_ordered":["قرب","يتم"],"tokens_ordered":["يتيما","ذا","مقربة"],"vec_preview":[-0.08910000324249268,0.08139999955892563,-0.06080000102519989,-0.013399999588727951,0.0015999999595806003,-0.05209999904036522,-0.02319999970495701,0.06809999793767929]},{"ayah_id":"90:16","surah":90,"ayah":16,"arabic":"أَوْ مِسْكِينًا ذَا مَتْرَبَةٍ","english":"Or the poverty-stricken destitute who is completely rundown (and homeless).","roots_ordered":["ترب","سكن"],"tokens_ordered":["مسكينا","ذا","متربة"],"vec_preview":[-0.01899999938905239,0.10249999910593033,-0.04179999977350235,0.007400000002235174,0.06440000236034393,-0.07509999722242355,-0.06199999898672104,0.061799999326467514]},{"ayah_id":"90:17","surah":90,"ayah":17,"arabic":"ثُمَّ كَانَ مِنَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالْمَرْحَمَةِ","english":"(Provided this striving soul is) one of those who believe and advise one another patience and tolerance and urge one another for mutual affection and mercy.","roots_ordered":["ٱلذي","امن","رحم","صبر","كون","وصي"],"tokens_ordered":["الذين","امنوا","وتواصوا","بالصبر","بالمرحمة"],"vec_preview":[-0.04600000008940697,0.08889999985694885,-0.09860000014305115,0.034699998795986176,0.042500000447034836,-0.0812000036239624,-0.043800000101327896,0.07190000265836716]},{"ayah_id":"90:18","surah":90,"ayah":18,"arabic":"أُولَـٰئِكَ أَصْحَابُ الْمَيْمَنَةِ","english":"These are the people of the Right Hand (i.e., the privileged and the pardoned).","roots_ordered":["صحب","يمن"],"tokens_ordered":["اصحاب","الميمنة"],"vec_preview":[-0.08780000358819962,0.08860000222921371,-0.06840000301599503,0.049300000071525574,0.01889999955892563,-0.0828000009059906,0.004800000227987766,0.0640999972820282]},{"ayah_id":"90:19","surah":90,"ayah":19,"arabic":"وَالَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا بِآيَاتِنَا هُمْ أَصْحَابُ الْمَشْأَمَةِ","english":"And those who reject Our signs are the people of the Left Hand (the callous and the doomed).","roots_ordered":["ٱلذي","